## General

### 10. Inspection Details
- **Method**: `GET`
- **Endpoint**: `/api/inspections/:id`
- **Used In**: `app/client/inspections/InspectionDetailsModal.tsx` & `app/agent/inspections/InspectionDetailsModal.tsx`
